# How to Install
```bash
# In terminal do:
$ pip install solvit
```

## Building from Source for Developers

```console
$ git clone https://github.com/TralahM/Solvit.git
$ cd Solvit
$ pip install -e .
```


## Input from a csv file of the Puzzle
